block content

    .container-fluid.qanda-headline-container
        .row.qanda-headline-row
            .col-12.qanda-headline-col 
                img.qanda-headline-img(src='/img/sectionCover-2.webp' alt='Image of Burgas Bulgaria landscape') 
                div.qanda-headline We Are Here To Answer Any Question
                button.section-headline-cta-btn.to-calendly-btn(aria-label='Go to the contact us page') Contact Us
    
    .container-fluid.qanda-questions-accordion-container
        .row.qanda-questions-headline-row.justify-content-center 
            .col-10.qanda-questions-headline-col 
                h1.qanda-questions-headline Questions and Answers
        .row.qanda-questions-accordion-row.justify-content-center 
            .col-10.qanda-questions-accordion-col
                #qandaAccordion.accordion.accordion-flush
                    div.accordion-item
                        h2.accordion-header
                            button.accordion-button(type='button' data-bs-toggle='collapse' data-bs-target='#collapseOne' aria-expanded='true' aria-controls='collapseOne' )
                                | What does the future hold for the global real estate market?
                        #collapseOne.accordion-collapse.collapse.show(data-bs-parent='#qandaAccordion')
                            .accordion-body According to forecasts from international real estate research firms, the global real estate market is expected to continue growing in the coming years. Demand for apartments and income-producing properties remains high, especially in areas with accelerated economic development and advanced infrastructure. <br> ● <strong>Stable Economy:</strong> Many countries worldwide are experiencing steady growth contributing to rising property values.<br> ● <strong>Investment Opportunities:</strong> Diverse options exist for real estate investment — from residential properties to commercial projects.<br> ● <strong>Rental Demand:</strong> Population growth and tourism create high demand for rental properties.<br> ● <strong>Innovation and Green Building:</strong> A global trend toward sustainability and innovation is influencing the design and construction of modern properties.
                    div.accordion-item
                        h2.accordion-header
                            button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button' data-bs-toggle='collapse' data-bs-target='#collapseTwo' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseTwo' )
                                | What are the advantages of investing in international real estate?
                        #collapseTwo.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent='#qandaAccordion')
                            .accordion-body Investing in international real estate allows for risk diversification, portfolio variety, and exposure to emerging markets. <br> ● <strong>High Yields:</strong> In many countries, attractive rental yields can be achieved.<br> ● <strong>Potential for Appreciation:</strong> Developing cities around the world offer steady growth in real estate prices.<br> ● <strong>Inflation Protection:</strong> Real estate investment is considered one of the safest ways to preserve capital value over time.<br> ● <strong>Diverse Options:</strong> Apartments, villas, commercial properties, vacation homes, and short-term rentals.
                    div.accordion-item
                        h2.accordion-header
                            button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button' data-bs-toggle='collapse' data-bs-target='#collapseThree' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseThree' )
                                | What types of properties can be found?
                        #collapseThree.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent='#qandaAccordion')
                            .accordion-body A wide variety of properties can be found globally, including:<br> ● <strong>New Apartments:</strong> New projects under construction or recently completed.<br> ● <strong>Commercial Properties:</strong> Offices, shops, and business centers.<br> ● <strong>Villas and Private Homes:</strong> Luxury properties in quiet or scenic areas.<br> ● <strong>Vacation Apartments:</strong> Properties in tourist areas for seasonal rental or personal use.
                    div.accordion-item
                        h2.accordion-header
                            button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button' data-bs-toggle='collapse' data-bs-target='#collapseFour' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseFour' )
                                | In which countries and regions can one invest in real estate?
                        #collapseFour.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent='#qandaAccordion')
                            .accordion-body The global real estate market offers diverse investment opportunities worldwide. Popular regions include: <br> ● <strong>Europe:</strong> Major cities such as Lisbon, Athens, and Barcelona attract many investors.<br> ● <strong>Asia:</strong> Countries like Thailand, Vietnam, and the Philippines offer rapid economic growth.<br> ● <strong>United States:</strong> A diverse market with opportunities for income-producing residential and commercial investments.<br> ● <strong>Middle East:</strong> Gulf countries are investing in innovative and luxury real estate development.
                    div.accordion-item
                        h2.accordion-header
                            button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button' data-bs-toggle='collapse' data-bs-target='#collapseFive' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseFive' )
                                | What does the process of purchasing a property abroad include?
                        #collapseFive.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent='#qandaAccordion')
                            .accordion-body The process of buying property abroad includes several main stages: <br> ● <strong>Choosing an Investment Destination:</strong> Identifying a country and region based on yield and budget.<br> ● <strong>Property Inspection:</strong> Comprehensive legal and professional inspection before purchase.<br> ● <strong>Contract Signing:</strong> Negotiation management and legal counsel.<br> ● <strong>Property Registration:</strong> Registration in the buyer's name according to local laws.<br> ● <strong>Property Management:</strong> Options for management and marketing services after the purchase.

